Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒法突然起跑什麼的… 是有多扯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人的妹妹！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那個 我什麼都沒聽到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結婚什麼的我都沒聽到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說謊爛得嚇死人啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.54,0:02:34.00,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,470)}#09 真是屈辱、被羞辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:34.00,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,470)\3c&HF2C855&\bord7}#09 真是屈辱、被羞辱了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請在100字以內簡潔回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 100字？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 話 還 沒 說 完 呢 給 我 稍 微…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}喂 你都說了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安靜啦！ 我都不知道數到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜和小紅可是有婚約的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你給我一邊涼快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥 婚約！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}耶～耶～ 活該吧你～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種事我又不可能會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}婚約是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 該不會紅緒大人的妹妹也跟我們是同族！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和紅緒大人是同伴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是被奇怪的毒氣污染了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人跟我們是同族的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒和小紅都不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 不是嗎 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那他們倆不是同族卻有婚約了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們也有自己的情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也有我的情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽囑咐過我要是找到同族的男性要馬上佔有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的情況關我啥事～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 那個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未續同學要白夜跟她結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就是說未續同學對白夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在想你剛剛跌倒要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不要緊啦 不過那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你來這邊沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看你們好像在討論有什麼重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重要的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是剛剛未續同學說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫你和她結婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「啊」算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我要跟小紅結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是說那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結婚！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼什麼 你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}婚約的事在學校要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}血痕 沾染著血的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有事件的味道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我才不會被騙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們還提到木葉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼什麼什麼啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 該不會是小紅和三峰在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 那你們提到木葉是在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去問本人就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以是怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想他是讓你去問未續同學的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉～ 你在哪～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺有點受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛剛那樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前你說過不要把婚約的事情跟其他人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是自己要他別把婚約的事情說出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被一口否認了卻受打擊什麼的 也太自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說我會受打擊也就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 到底是怎樣啦 那個叫未續的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超失禮的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}火大…好火大啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未續同學原本是找真白有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是什麼事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她問我進城是不是因為看中了紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是屈辱 被羞辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被羞辱了是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該不會是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不敢相信 那小不點是怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然無法理解紅緒大人有多出色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種人居然還生活在紅緒大人的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到木葉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶吶 我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅和三峰提到木葉是在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 提到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是在嘲笑我在走廊大喊大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和小不點爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有我不知道他們倆有婚約還去求婚的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉 振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 看看紅緒大人的照片
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 我問了小紅和三峰有沒有在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被否認了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是他們倆一直都在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還以為這能成為一個不錯的八卦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人妹妹的戀人曝光什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 不是有婚約的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 雖是說婚約 其實是那種的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是很常見的那種父母擅自決定的婚約呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然當事人不願意 那我也還有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}復活！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話題歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到最後還是不明白是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟我結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說末續同學喜歡白夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然有了證據照片 說服力就會上一個檔次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13.342\fs50\c&H63BAE8&\pos(504,583)\3c&H8157B2&\shad0}頂級機密領域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有點事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 昨天和末續幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是因為紅緒 害我受了天大的屈辱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要怎麼賠償我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然不太明白 但我會負責的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是無法理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼紅緒大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 害羞了 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}於是呢 其實是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次總該告訴我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人氣爆棚的姐姐大人總是去找真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以您身邊的人吃醋了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我想您是不是不要總是去找真白比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是竟然為了我引發了紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是悲傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是跟末續關照一聲比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了 會把事情搞得更麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概已經沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是末續同學誤會了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為真白一直在躲著姐姐大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎… 呃…咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我和真白碳很要好所以吃醋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以難道說 小紅也在吃醋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是的 沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃？ 咦…小紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回來的時候去買雞蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天做戚風蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在網路上有看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好想嚐嚐那個巧克力戚風蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人也喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就做巧克力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一說和姐姐大人一樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然真白可能不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但姐姐也是有很多優點的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事都能做到 很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人氣很高也是值得高興的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的話可能與其說是吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該說是有點寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然還要讓妹妹為她操心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說起來 就因為同族很少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就突然要白夜和她結婚 她到底在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經告訴她小紅和白夜有婚約了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你告訴她婚約的事了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣我會很頭疼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是很好嗎 雙親公認的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正大光明一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是如果傳出八卦我會很頭疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是被大野同學聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可能又會被追著不放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去囑咐她不要外傳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她會乖乖聽話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會放棄是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是說紅緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然末續同學是喜歡白夜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}擔心婚約的事情會被大肆宣揚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊… 雖然也有這個原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}親自去拜託一下不行的話就談條件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}賄賂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}賄賂！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}照片怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個人不是拿著很多紅緒的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然不知道用來幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要多給她看看紅緒的怪相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定會醒悟過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺主旨有點偏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去拍就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒的怪相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}潛行可是我的拿手好戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總…總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去拜託她不要把婚約的事情說出去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生會的工作請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天也一同度過祥和的學園生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒教派…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然真白碳的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是傲嬌沒錯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘴上說對紅緒大人不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果卻是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然嘴上說了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是經受不起紅緒大人的魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是既然這樣也要給窩有個相應的態度啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在學校裡還真是沒什麼破綻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 這個 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我是紅緒的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以連我也被討厭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事呀 找我有什麼事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找我有何貴幹呀 真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你瞎搞個啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你才搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那個 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是因為我大放厥詞說了不會放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}關於和白夜婚約的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你能保密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是不願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒也沒打算去大肆宣揚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是未婚夫你卻跟仁子說沒有和三峰交往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}並且還叫我保守這個秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說你不願意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不願意的話 解除婚約如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣對男方也有失禮數
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果婚約解除了 我也就能遵從媽媽的叮囑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能和同族結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛剛那樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也知道這樣有失禮數…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎麼哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是很不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是末續同學的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是我把她弄哭了一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道我要遭難了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事的 就是垃圾吹進了眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不得了 去保健室嗎 要不去眼科看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 末續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們關係很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯呢 畢竟是同屆的 最近經常聊天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嘛 那小紅就承蒙照顧了 末續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有真白也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她就像是我可愛的妹妹一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請跟她們好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…那再見啦 末續同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放學後見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眼睛進了垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅那可愛的眼睛裡面進了垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眼睛進了垃圾…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太誇張了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是說校內清掃工作沒有做好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 在今後的每一小時裡設立一次清掃活動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我會在會議上提案的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別做那種濫用職權的事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這也是為了學校好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 趁現在拍下她的怪相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要和小紅在一起就經常出現古怪言行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}校內環境整潔也會增加舒適感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}露餡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你那是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然真白碳的態度是傲嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全不對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人要我和小不點和睦相處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嘛 俗話說越吵架關係越和睦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不和睦呢 我說的不是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和睦相處有什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟真白和小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時她為什麼會哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 戚風蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我開動了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 軟綿綿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請從我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個給真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的照片 看你很想要的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都說了上次不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}簽名… 自己設計的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然哭了出來 給末續同學添麻煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得去道歉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對男方也有失禮數
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼 想再拿一些棒子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說啊 我做了蛋糕要不要嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有做得太甜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 味道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種甜度就沒問題了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 關於婚約的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之所以請你保密是因為怕傳開了被人戲弄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃…就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}並不是討厭婚約的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是說 小紅是在說她也喜歡白夜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是木訥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請再給我一塊蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}終於到來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嬌羞期！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是這個意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,0)\an7\c&H543AD8&}\N恭\N祝 {\c&H000000&}\N嬌\N羞\N期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後呢 要說到是不是好事… 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很好哦 是好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就像升級了一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}升級？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你個子太大…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒看清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}個…個子太大沒看清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你幹什麼啊 紅緒真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先不說這個 馬上就到白色情人節了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是男人大展身手的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情人節那天有收到小紅的巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次就由白夜送禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一口氣拉近兩人的距離吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那一刻我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冰箱裡的牛奶今天過期這件事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是家庭主婦嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那一刻我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳小內內上的貓咪今天變成了兩隻這件事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喵！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下回 查了一下嬌羞期這個詞
